Targets intermediate DIY enthusiasts who have done gel manicures before but new to magnetic polish. They understand cure times, base coats, prep but need magnetic-specific guidance. Appeals to 25-40 age range planning Valentine's nail looks, want salon-quality at home, willing to practice technique.

